-- BMW Sales Probably Rose at Double-Digit Pace This Month, Sales Chief Says
-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 2010-09-30T11:04:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/bmw-sales-probably-rose-at-double-digit-pace-this-month-sales-chief-says.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG, the
world’s largest maker of luxury cars, said September deliveries
probably grew at a double-digit pace, according to sales chief
Ian Robertson. China sales this year will top BMW’s target for
120,000 vehicles, he said at the Paris Motor Show today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
